sense.def:
V kraju, vozilu ali posodi, ki je
empty
, ni oseb ali stvari.

Gib, grožnja ali odnos, ki je
empty
, je brez pomena.

seg.quote: They ignored his threats as empty rhetoric.

sense.def:
Če za človekovo življenje ali obdobje rečemo, da je
empty
, hočemo povedati, da se v njem ne dogaja nič zanimivega ali vrednega.

seg.quote: How shall I exist during the empty days ahead?

sense.def:
To empty a container
pomeni odstraniti vsebino neke posode.

seg.quote: She picked up an ashtray and emptied it into a wastepaper basket.

sense.def:
To empty a substance or object out of a container
pomeni zliti ali stresti neko snov iz posode.

seg.quote: Empty the water out of those boots.

sense.def:
Kadar neki prostor
empties
, gredo vsi iz njega.

seg.quote: The play was over and the auditorium began to empty.

sense.def:
Kadar posoda
empties
, vse steče ali izgine iz nje.
